{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01V5UDLGo25m5wz47qccAPyn","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\"\n     2→         xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n     3→         xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\">\n     4→  <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>\n     5→\n     6→  <groupId>jakarta.tutorial</groupId>\n     7→  <artifactId>roster</artifactId>\n     8→  <version>1.0.0</version>\n     9→  <packaging>pom</packaging>\n    10→  <name>roster</name>\n    11→\n    12→  <properties>\n    13→    <maven.compiler.release>17</maven.compiler.release>\n    14→    <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>\n    15→    <liberty.version>24.0.0.12</liberty.version>\n    16→  </properties>\n    17→\n    18→  <dependencyManagement>\n    19→    <dependencies>\n    20→      <dependency>\n    21→        <groupId>io.openliberty.features</groupId>\n    22→        <artifactId>features-bom</artifactId>\n    23→        <version>${liberty.version}</version>\n    24→        <type>pom</type>\n    25→        <scope>import</scope>\n    26→      </dependency>\n    27→    </dependencies>\n    28→  </dependencyManagement>\n    29→\n    30→  <modules>\n    31→    <module>roster-common</module>\n    32→    <module>roster-ejb</module>\n    33→    <module>roster-appclient</module>\n    34→    <module>roster-web</module>\n    35→    <module>roster-ear</module>\n    36→  </modules>\n    37→\n    38→  <build>\n    39→    <pluginManagement>\n    40→      <plugins>\n    41→        <plugin>\n    42→          <groupId>io.openliberty.tools</groupId>\n    43→          <artifactId>liberty-maven-plugin</artifactId>\n    44→          <version>3.11.1</version>\n    45→        </plugin>\n    46→      </plugins>\n    47→    </pluginManagement>\n    48→  </build>\n    49→</project>\n    50→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhen